						<strong>Hero House Cleaning Recurring Discounts:</strong>
						<ul>
							<li>Weekly cleaning: <strong>20% off</strong></li>
							<li>Bi-weekly cleaning: <strong>15% off</strong></li>
							<li>Monthly cleaning: <strong>10% off</strong></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<p class="factor-tip"><strong>Money-saving tip:</strong> Even monthly recurring service saves you 10% compared to one-time bookings.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="factor-card">
					<div class="factor-icon">🏠</div>
					<h3>Home Condition</h3>
					<p>A cluttered or heavily soiled home takes longer to clean. Excessive pet hair, visible dirt buildup, or significant disorganization increases cleaning time and cost.</p>
					<p class="factor-tip"><strong>Money-saving tip:</strong> Do a quick declutter and pickup before cleaners arrive - it allows them to focus on actual cleaning rather than organizing.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="factor-card">
					<div class="factor-icon">🔧</div>
					<h3>Add-On Services</h3>
					<p>Special requests beyond standard cleaning affect the price. Common add-ons include interior windows ($30-$80), inside refrigerator ($25-$40), carpet cleaning (varies by room), and laundry services.</p>
					<p class="factor-tip"><strong>Money-saving tip:</strong> Bundle add-ons with deep cleaning rather than requesting them separately.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="factor-card">
					<div class="factor-icon">📍</div>
