					<p>Some companies charge travel fees for homes outside central Knoxville. West Knoxville, Farragut, and Oak Ridge may incur additional charges with some providers.</p>
					<p class="factor-tip"><strong>At Hero House Cleaning:</strong> We serve all of Knoxville and surrounding areas with no hidden travel fees included in your quote.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="factor-card">
					<div class="factor-icon">⚡</div>
					<h3>Urgency & Timing</h3>
					<p>Same-day or next-day service may cost 15-25% more due to schedule adjustments. Weekend and evening appointments may also carry premium pricing with some companies.</p>
					<p class="factor-tip"><strong>Money-saving tip:</strong> Book 3-5 days in advance when possible and be flexible with timing.</p>
